						               													<description>This scenario pack subtitled &amp;quot;SS I No Quarter, No Glory / SS II F&amp;uuml;hrer's Firemen&amp;quot;, is an update for the out of print scenario packs Waffen SS: No Quarter No Glory and Waffen SS: Fuhrer's Firemen.  This pack contains 14 scenarios that have been updated with the errata and tweaked for play balance.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Unlike the original scenario packs, this publication does not include any counter sheets.  The counter sheets that were included in the original scenario packs were deemed too similar to the AH/MMP counter art, and is part of the reason why the original scenario packs are no longer in print.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This scenario pack is compatible with the AH/MMP ASL Game System, and components from that game system are required to play these scenarios.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Scenarios: NQNG 1 to 6, FF 7 to 14&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
